</ol>
<p>The post <a href="https://www.gutmicrobiotaforhealth.com/paving-the-way-for-microbiome-based-therapy-in-clinical-practice/">Paving the way for microbiome-based therapy in clinical practice</a> appeared first on <a href="https://www.gutmicrobiotaforhealth.com">Gut Microbiota for Health</a>.</p>
