		<title>How what you eat, the medications you take, and where you live shape your gut microbiota</title>
		<link>https://www.gutmicrobiotaforhealth.com/how-what-you-eat-the-medications-you-take-and-where-you-live-shape-your-gut-microbiota/</link>
		
		<dc:creator><![CDATA[Giovana Martucelli]]></dc:creator>
		<pubDate>Wed, 11 Jun 2025 07:49:04 +0000</pubDate>
